// @see https://www.imgix.com/docs/reference
export const PARAMS_EXP_MAP = Object.freeze({
  // Adjustment
  brightness: "bri",
  contrast: "con",
  exposure: "exp",
  gamma: "gam",
  highlights: "high",
  hue: "hue",
  invert: "invert",
  saturation: "sat",
  shaddows: "shad",
  shadows: "shad",
  sharpness: "sharp",
  "unsharp-mask": "usm",
  "unsharp-radius": "usmrad",
  vibrance: "vib",

  // Automatic
  "auto-features": "auto",

  // Background
  "background-color": "bg",

  // Blend
  blend: "blend",
  "blend-mode": "bm",
  "blend-align": "ba",
  "blend-alpha": "balph",
  "blend-padding": "bp",
  "blend-width": "bw",
  "blend-height": "bh",
  "blend-fit": "bf",
  "blend-crop": "bc",
  "blend-size": "bs",
  "blend-x": "bx",
  "blend-y": "by",

  // Border & Padding
  border: "border",
  padding: "pad",

  // Face Detection
  "face-index": "faceindex",
  "face-padding": "facepad",
  faces: "faces",

  // Format
  "chroma-subsampling": "chromasub",
  "color-quantization": "colorquant",
  download: "dl",
  DPI: "dpi",
  format: "fm",
  "lossless-compression": "lossless",
  quality: "q",

  // Mask
  "mask-image": "mask",

  // Mask
  "noise-blur": "nr",
  "noise-sharpen": "nrs",

  // Palette n/a
  // PDF n/a
  // Pixel Density n/a

  // Rotation
  "flip-direction": "flip",
  orientation: "or",
  "rotation-angle": "rot",

  // Size
  "crop-mode": "crop",
  "fit-mode": "fit",
  "image-height": "h",
  "image-width": "w",

  // Stylize
  blurring: "blur",
  halftone: "htn",
  monotone: "mono",
  pixelate: "px",
  "sepia-tone": "sepia",

  // Trim TODO
  // Watermark TODO

  // Extra
  height: "h",
  width: "w",
});
